Death valley.

1836
01:26:35,538 --> 01:26:37,453
Whatever.
Brian's doing the show.

1837
01:26:37,496 --> 01:26:39,237
You're gonna be
the staff.

1838
01:26:39,281 --> 01:26:40,282
