incredible opportunity.

1846
01:26:53,295 --> 01:26:55,427
He doesn't want to do it.
We do.

1847
01:26:55,471 --> 01:26:56,298
Whoa, whoa, whoa.

1848
01:26:56,341 --> 01:26:58,387
Why do you
get to be Brian?

1849
